{
  "stem": "10359.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time I could-- I tried to sell some of the furniture, piano, this and that or some of the materials we had from home from the drugstore left over to exchange it for gold coins, like [INAUDIBLE] into Mexican pesos, things like that.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because gold was the more or less exchange for any goods.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I tried to accumulate as much as I could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's what happened after the second part.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, since I knew that this is the beginning of the end, it looked like to me like it's twilight zone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't know where the heck I am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So one of my teachers in high school used to be a Ukrainian professor of Latin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he became a mayor of the city of Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I tried-- through him and some other people-- they took out some documents from high school, Polish documents, of some sons of the offic-- Polish officers who fled to Poland when the Soviets came.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were more or less my age.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So on the basis of their birth certificate and school things, they made for me false papers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The the name that I assumed is actually an actual name of a-- of a-- of a man who was my age, who going to school.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But his parents were in the army, they left when the Soviets came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you know him?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they-- Dorothy too was based-- her documents are based on papers which are factual papers of birth certificates and high school records and so forth.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had to pay for it, naturally, with gold coins.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But nobody-- first of all, people had an idea that nothing will happen, that maybe this is just a passing thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything will get organized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They wouldn't kill everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They already killed everybody, so they'll let those people go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I figured, just in case, let me make some papers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I was the only one, I think-- I think the only one in Ostrog who did it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I also tried through some friends to establish some points of escape in case of something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now I had a-- my friend that we went to high school together, but he was in the lower grade.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was teaching him German and, and Latin, and I was very close to his family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the other friend that we formed that group in high school, the jazz singing group, they helped me a lot later on after I escaped.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, after the second Aktion, my sister was in Rovno, which was about 40 miles from my town of Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Her husband was killed by the Soviets because he was a known Zionist leader of the Betar.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So she, from Lviv, she-- because he studied law.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she came to Rovno where my relatives on my mother's side lived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I tried to go to her to bring her back to my hometown to Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But when I came, this was late-- I remember it was late November because it was raining and snowing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I had holes in my boots.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I came to Rovno, and I was a little bit too late.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They already surrounded the area where the Jews lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I had to escape and walk the streets, did-- not knowing where am I going.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because if they would find me there-- even though I had some paperss-- I had no place to sleep over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was raining, snowing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I was cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Luckily that I met my friend from that singing group who was in charge of a theater in Rovno.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he was surprised to see me, but he took me right in, put me in the basement.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Got in touch with some other people from my hometown.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They sent this horse and wagon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they took me up from the basement during the night and brought me back to Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That's the fellow that I visited in Warsaw several years ago.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Now he became Vice Minister of Culture in Poland after the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he was very happy to see me and all that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The other friend of mine who helped me tremendously, the, the one that I was tutoring, and was still from high school, he had-- he had cousins in a city, again, 20, 30 miles from Rovno.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I told him in case I need something, he should introduce me that I'm his second or third cousin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Now, after we escaped from the ghetto-- this was the third Aktion when they finished all the, the massacres-- I escaped that time under false papers because Dorothy was wounded in the leg.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he helped me to establish contact with those of his cousins.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
